Hello @pemontto, we currently updating Google Sheets to[ version 2](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/pull/3948), do you interesting in continue this PR and merging with old version? There was some unresolved issues, that has to be fixed, if you not interesting in continuing we can close it for now.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/88898367/195274537-5483742b-4d43-4ef7-946c-8db49411c383.png)

and after fixing it some issues still exists:
- updating using column with not unique keys:  update data when keys is not unique, read sheet → update values in set node → use it output to update sheet

- updating rows that match key with some value: with updateAll on provide id and value in set node → update all occurrences of this id in sheet

